library(MA.DBDS)

Test the package works by running

test = generate_example()
## Performing NN search on 2 features using 50 neighbors...
## NN search complete...
## density calculated...
## normalizing densities...
## performing density-based downsampling...
## complete!

You can run it on your dataset using:

df_dbds = MA.DBDS::performKNN_DensityBasedDownsampling(input.data = test,downsample_n = 50,features = c('x','y'))
## Performing NN search on 2 features using 25 neighbors...
## NN search complete...
## density calculated...
## normalizing densities...
## performing density-based downsampling...
## complete!
